Package UI

Class Summary
JFrameMBTAHelper The graphics for the application; Sets up the JFrame for the JPanels used in the rest of the application
JPanelChangeData JPanel in which the user chooses the source of the data.
JPanelLineColorSelector JPanel in which user selects the Line Color; Used in JPanels where a line needs to be selected, with the exception of data source selection.
JPanelMap JPanel that displays a map of the MBTA T System.
JPanelNextArrival JPanel used for the NextArrival functionality; User selects a Line Color, and the stops for which he/she wishes to view the next train arrivals
JPanelPlanTrip JPanel for the Plan Trip (Find Routes) functionality
JPanelStopSelector JPanel for selecting stops; Used in NextArrivals and PlanTrip panels
JPanelTimePicker JPanel for selecting a time
JPanelTrainLocations JPanel used for the (Find) Train Locations functionality
JPanelTrainStops JPanel for finding the names of all stops on a line
JPanelTripSelector JPanel used to select all the options for finding a route
